# Copy to .env and fill in values from Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API
#
# Production cloud project: idtygsydzixnswntbign
# Variable names use UNDERSCORES: SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY (not SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE-KEY)
#
# Vercel Production — required now:
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL, VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY, VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID
#   SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
#
# Vercel — optional until you need employee admin (/api/employees/*):
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
#
# Verify: GET /api/healthz/env → ok:true (apiReady:false without service role is OK)

# --- Cloud production (idtygsydzixnswntbign) ---
